{"tid":806244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］如果你係柯南(新一) 你會揀小蘭，灰原定係步美？","createTime":"2018-09-04T13:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T04:04:46.000Z","uid":48577,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1556522c84a51aeae9db903cd758a578e2a886b6","tid":806244,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"假設你已組搵到APTX-4689嘅解藥 可以隨時變番大個做工藤新一 你會點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小蘭：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/210434_842ef2916e1177529aa6bf96cad5c14b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F210434_842ef2916e1177529aa6bf96cad5c14b.png&h=7bda130b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/205743_891be552065cfa37574cdeddaa4106cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F205743_891be552065cfa37574cdeddaa4106cb.png&h=b82f4ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n名副其實既青梅竹馬，應該係大家都夢寐以求<br />\n又識煮飯煲湯，你消失左大半年唔見人都冇搵第二個，專一又賢妻feel；可惜係佢空手道太勁 你唔夠佢抽 亦有可能隨時打死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n灰原：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/210404_79e6f0dc8210432ce97aef72b5846ed0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F210404_79e6f0dc8210432ce97aef72b5846ed0.png&h=0717bd19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/211147_a0b852a0d80d15bcb3b2fd49a0627197.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F211147_a0b852a0d80d15bcb3b2fd49a0627197.png&h=e7cc6875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家都同病相憐，變左細路，所以某程度上好明白大家感受。對於被追殺嘅佢來講得番柯南同博士呢個靠山 同埋有幾次比柯南救左命之後暗戀柯南。佢表面上睇落好毒舌成日串柯南但實際上當有事發生會肯出來幫佢擋刀擋子彈，俗d講姐係傲嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n步美：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/211802_f88135b6ca51c48e47dc9290fca3e916.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F211802_f88135b6ca51c48e47dc9290fca3e916.png&h=6c53e64c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真人版宣萱 十次綁架九次都係綁佢，次次柯南想一個人行動硬係要死跟著佢 同元太光彥果隊偵探團成日搞搞震(我個人想佢地死好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 出事果陣淨係識亂叫同喊 盲既都睇得出佢暗戀柯南 但另一方面光彥又擺到明鍾意步美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢d三角關係我唔識呀<br />\n<br />\n綜合以上資料， 你地點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋歡迎補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506f876527dd7c7d05afc8dcfbfb9364c441904c","tid":806244,"uid":48577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T13:47:11.000Z","msg":"補充泳裝圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/214528_d05a1e6f94516e5c930a8eca6a0613be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F214528_d05a1e6f94516e5c930a8eca6a0613be.png&h=e49f28e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/214532_b578566fe5fa397da0a5197ac7d7dee9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F214532_b578566fe5fa397da0a5197ac7d7dee9.png&h=7dafdfa7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/214541_f36490fde662e295d6519f22a0439909.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F214541_f36490fde662e295d6519f22a0439909.png&h=77abf04a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/214546_0882a9b96aae4ff40fc01aed0a95f24e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F214546_0882a9b96aae4ff40fc01aed0a95f24e.png&h=002ce828&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/214621_ad2aa3d27f7f18114a1844fc337a3a7c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F214621_ad2aa3d27f7f18114a1844fc337a3a7c.png&h=64877aea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d510b8c32b18f59f60c5229efa6e68658b96a6fc","tid":806244,"uid":188333,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"小蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 長頭髮嘅女仔最吸引"},{"pid":"711ba01a4ada9ae264c8a6f157cc5f42df5f13ac","tid":806244,"uid":171621,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"灰原<br />\n唔知點解硬係覺得灰原同柯南最夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97e770aca6e79387777f13a55ebb567840c2f19","tid":806244,"uid":67896,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T14:01:45.000Z","msg":"灰原啦 聰明過小蘭咁多"},{"pid":"d03e33bc0c54abf2d44bb80c7e0127ef6afa5f00","tid":806244,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"唔俾解藥灰原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e9b3a22efc5964c438edf6d4d128eb711bf91e","tid":806244,"uid":169468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d03e33bc0c54abf2d44bb80c7e0127ef6afa5f00","tid":806244,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"唔俾解藥灰原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T14:02:58.000Z","msg":"合法蘿莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touc